text: Jules Lecoutre (24 April 1878 - 18 April 1962) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1878 births Category:1962 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:People from Tourcoing
